Class AtakBroadcast.DocumentedIntentFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.IntentFilter
      • com.atakmap.android.ipc.AtakBroadcast.DocumentedIntentFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    Enclosing class:
    AtakBroadcast
    public static class AtakBroadcast.DocumentedIntentFilter
extends android.content.IntentFilter
    Instead of using IntentFilters, ATAK makes use of DocumentedIntentFilter to provide for automatic extraction of documentation supplied by the developer.
